cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a deep learning solution for automated scoring of PD-L1 expression in NSCLC needle biopsies, which involves image analysis and classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of semi-supervised learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Deep Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval and analysis of medical images, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
